# Loyalty — Cron Expiry Warning Trigger (M11-S06)
# Publishes the cron-loyalty-expiry-warning trigger, dispatched to
# NotifyExpiringPointsTriggerHandler (M17-S03), which publishes one PointsExpiringSoon event per
# customer with points expiring within 7 days. In production, Cloud Scheduler publishes the same
# trigger directly to Pub/Sub weekly (Mondays 06:00 UTC) — this endpoint is the local/manual
# trigger path only, protected by the global InternalApiGuard (X-Internal-Key), not
# PubSubPushGuard.
# Response is { ok: true } once the trigger is published — it does not wait for the job to
# finish. Requires the Pub/Sub emulator running (pnpm infra:up).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /cron/loyalty-expiry-warning — publish the weekly expiry-warning trigger
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/loyalty-expiry-warning
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###
